										<div class="text">
											<p>The API powering <a href="https://www.moneysupermarket.com/new-boiler/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Money Supermarket's New Boiler comparison</a> was originally created by yours truly before being sold to them.</p>
											<p>Working alongside multiple heating system providers across the country I processed and transposed a questionnaire before sending it to various APIs.</p>
											<p>The resulting listings were converted to a standardised format and returned to be displayed on the website/emails/etc.</p>
										</div>
									</div>
									<label class="arrowRight" for="slide2pro"></label>
								</div>
