											<p><a href="https://cddastory.jarfjam.co.uk/" target="_blank">CDDA Story Browser</a></p>
											<p>Cataclysm: Dark Days Ahead is an open source community built videogame that is constantly being updated. In the game are various snippets of lore to be found in the form of scribbled notes, media files and more that I find to be very interesting.</p>
											<p>I've created a system that parses through the game files to retrieve these snippets of lore for easy viewing via the website.</p>
